{
  "texts": [
    "Note that the parameter sets presented herein are intended as illustrative examples.",
    "They may not necessarily represent optimal configurations for the individual libraries and are not intended for comparison among libraries.",
    "Table 5.4 and 5.5 provide examples of parameter sets for (RNS variants of) BGV/BFV in an SHE setting, i.e., without bootstrapping.",
    "The parameters were estimated to illustrate the Category 128, 192, or 256 security levels.",
    "The notation used in both tables is described in Table 5.1."
  ]
}